BT feat. JES - Every Other Way

Simple chords, as with my other songs :) I was inspired to put this up after hearing a 
cover of the song on YouTube by Michelle Do, found here: http://youtu.be/874WmmFHZlo
When I couldn't find the chords on here, I said she should put them up, unless she would 
rather I put them up and give her credit. She said it was fine with her for me to put 
them up, so yeah. Just to clear that up in case I got accused of stealing these from her :)

With the second D of the chorus, you could play Bm7 to give a bit of variation, but it's 
not necessary - it's down to personal preference really, both work.

Standard tuning.
Capo on 2nd fret.
